---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Svg1 from "../components/svg/Svg1.svelte";
import Svg2 from "../components/svg/Svg2.svelte";
import Journey1Svg from "../components/svg/Journey1Svg.svelte";
import Journey2Svg from "../components/svg/Journey2Svg.svelte";
import Journey3Svg from "../components/svg/Journey3Svg.svelte";
import Journey4Svg from "../components/svg/Journey4Svg.svelte";
import Journey5Svg from "../components/svg/Journey5Svg.svelte";
---

<Layout>
  <section class="p-2.5 lg:p-5 space-y-2.5 lg:space-y-5">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-2.5 lg:gap-5">
      <div class="bg-gray-500"></div>
      <div>
        <h1
          class="font-star relative z-10 text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-5xl 2xl:text-7xl"
        >
          DOING FOR AI<br />WHAT WE DID<br />FOR THE WEB
        </h1>
        <div class="-mt-2.5 lg:-mt-5"><Svg1 /></div>
        <div class="-mt-2.5 lg:-mt-5"><Svg2 /></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p>
      Mozilla is transforming for a new era, doing for AI what we once did for
      the web: decentralizing control, empowering people with choice, and
      proving that an economic model anchored in a double bottom line of mission
      and money can succeed. At a moment when Big Tech seeks to monopolize the
      AI future, Mozilla is choosing a different path.
    </p>
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-2.5 lg:gap-5">
      <div class="lg:col-start-2">
        <a class="btn w-full border-black!" href="/stakes">
          Choose your future
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="p-2.5 lg:p-5">
    <hr class="border-dashed mb-2.5 lg:mb-5" />
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-4 gap-2.5 lg:gap-5">
      <div class="lg:col-start-2 lg:col-span-2 space-y-2.5 lg:space-y-5">
        <p>THE JOURNEY AHEAD</p>
        <p>
          The experience unfolds through six chapters - each a choice, each a
          signal of how we can build a different future together.
        </p>
        <h2 class="font-star text-5xl uppercase mt-7.5">
          “We're not here to predict the future. We're here to prove that in the
          age of artificial intelligence, we still get to choose its direction.”
        </h2>
        <p>– Nabiha Syed</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="p-2.5 lg:p-5">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-4 gap-px">
      <div
        class="lg:col-span-full p-2.5 lg:p-5 outline outline-dashed bg-yellow"
      >
        <h2 class="font-star text-7xl text-center">THE JOURNEY</h2>
      </div>
      <div
        class="relative overflow-hidden lg:col-span-2 outline outline-dashed bg-yellow"
      >
        <img
          class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 w-full h-1/2 object-cover object-top"
          src="/dots.png"
        />
        <div class="absolute bottom-2.5 left-2.5"><Journey1Svg /></div>
        <a
          class="relative flex-1 px-2.5 pt-2.t lg:px-5 lg:pt-5 pb-20 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center space-y-2.5"
          href="/stakes"
        >
          <span>I</span>
          <h3 class="font-tuoi-tre text-7xl uppercase">Stakes</h3>
          <p>Closed AI vs. Open AI. Which future will we choose?</p>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div
        class="relative overflow-hidden lg:col-span-2 outline outline-dashed bg-yellow"
      >
        <img
          class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 w-full h-1/2 object-cover object-top"
          src="/dots.png"
        />
        <div class="absolute bottom-2.5 right-2.5"><Journey2Svg /></div>
        <a
          class="relative flex-1 px-2.5 pt-2.t lg:px-5 lg:pt-5 pb-20 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center space-y-2.5"
          href="/code"
        >
          <span>II</span>
          <h3 class="font-workbench text-7xl uppercase">Code</h3>
          <p>Closed AI vs. Open AI. Which future will we choose?</p>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div
        class="relative overflow-hidden lg:col-span-2 outline outline-dashed bg-yellow"
      >
        <img
          class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 w-full h-1/2 object-cover object-top"
          src="/dots.png"
        />
        <div class="absolute bottom-2.5 right-2.5"><Journey3Svg /></div>
        <a
          class="relative flex-1 px-2.5 pt-2.t lg:px-5 lg:pt-5 pb-20 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center space-y-2.5"
          href="/tools"
        >
          <span>III</span>
          <h3 class="font-mainframe text-7xl uppercase">Tools</h3>
          <p>Closed AI vs. Open AI. Which future will we choose?</p>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div
        class="relative overflow-hidden lg:col-span-2 outline outline-dashed bg-yellow"
      >
        <img
          class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 w-full h-1/2 object-cover object-top"
          src="/dots.png"
        />
        <div class="absolute bottom-2.5 left-2.5"><Journey4Svg /></div>
        <a
          class="relative flex-1 px-2.5 pt-2.t lg:px-5 lg:pt-5 pb-20 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center space-y-2.5"
          href="/rebels"
        >
          <span>IV</span>
          <h3 class="font-computer text-7xl uppercase">Rebels</h3>
          <p>Closed AI vs. Open AI. Which future will we choose?</p>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div
        class="relative overflow-hidden lg:col-span-2 lg:col-start-2 outline outline-dashed bg-yellow"
      >
        <img
          class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 w-full h-1/2 object-cover object-top"
          src="/dots.png"
        />
        <div class="absolute bottom-2.5 right-2.5"><Journey5Svg /></div>
        <a
          class="relative flex-1 px-2.5 pt-2.t lg:px-5 lg:pt-5 pb-20 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center space-y-2.5"
          href="/ledger"
        >
          <span>V</span>
          <h3 class="font-star text-7xl uppercase">Ledger</h3>
          <p>Closed AI vs. Open AI. Which future will we choose?</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="p-2.5 lg:p-5">
    <hr class="border-dashed mb-2.5 lg:mb-5" />
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
      <div class="space-y-2.5">
        <p>2025 Audited Financial Statement</p>
        <a
          target="_blank"
          href=""
          class="btn invert inline-flex! items-center space-x-1.5 w-full lg:w-2/3"
        >
          <svg
            class="size-3"
            viewBox="0 0 313 313"
            fill="currentColor"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          >
            <path
              d="M0 196.49V312.86H312.97V196.74H273.64V273.46H37.88V196.49H0Z"
            ></path>
            <path
              d="M156.31 235.02C129.85 195.33 104.77 157.72 77.75 117.22H116.77V0H194.86V116.91H234.95C207.86 157.58 182.97 194.97 156.31 235.02Z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
          <span>Download report</span>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-2.5">
        <p>2025 Form 990</p>
        <a
          target="_blank"
          href=""
          class="btn invert inline-flex! items-center space-x-1.5 w-full lg:w-2/3"
        >
          <svg
            class="size-3"
            viewBox="0 0 313 313"
            fill="currentColor"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          >
            <path
              d="M0 196.49V312.86H312.97V196.74H273.64V273.46H37.88V196.49H0Z"
            ></path>
            <path
              d="M156.31 235.02C129.85 195.33 104.77 157.72 77.75 117.22H116.77V0H194.86V116.91H234.95C207.86 157.58 182.97 194.97 156.31 235.02Z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
          <span>Download report</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
